abstract: >-
  A reproducible runbook to deploy a persistent web terminal (ttyd + tmux)
  on macOS, gated by Cloudflare Zero Trust (email OTP) with Nerd Font glyphs
  served from Cloudflare R2. Designed for single-prompt automated setup via
  Claude Code, while remaining a readable runbook for manual execution.
